<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Thank you for getting an insurance quote from Kingsbridge.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>By now you’ll have had a chance to review the information in your quotation documents.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you have any&nbsp;<b>questions or concerns&nbsp;</b>about your potential policy,&nbsp;<b>need to amend any of the information</b>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<b>want to proceed with your purchase</b>&nbsp;reply to this email or give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
